    <p class="page-header__num">01 / 04</p>
    <h1 class="page-header__title">Education</h1>
    <p class="page-header__desc">
      My experience in education comes from both observing classrooms and stepping into a teaching role,
	  primarily in STEM and technology-focused environments.
	  I have supported and led lessons for middle school students,
	  helping them learn tools like CAD and guiding them through hands-on projects.
	  I have taught lessons such as using specific CAD tools step by step, where students
	  created their own designs and applied what they learned.Beyond individual lessons,
	  I have been involved in project-based learning units focused on design, modeling,
	  and problem solving. These projects included topics like robotics, reverse engineering,
	  and basic coding, all centered around real-world application. My approach to teaching focuses
	  on hands-on learning, collaboration, and helping students work through challenges rather than
	  just giving them answers. Overall, my experience has helped me develop a teaching style that prioritizes 
	  engagement, real skill development, and strong support for different learning needs.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="projects">

      <article class="project reveal">
        <div class="project__thumb">
          <img src="images/RiverCleanup.jpg" alt="River cleanup project" />
        </div>
        <div class="project__body">
          <p class="project__tag">Project</p>
          <h3 class="project__title">River Cleanup</h3>
          <p class="project__desc">A locally based and targeted lesson plan. The main goal was to connect all parts of STEM together in one lesson, effectively.</p>
          <div class="project__links">
            <a class="project__link" href="#">Write-up (PDF)</a>
            <a class="project__link" href="#">Photos</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="project reveal">
        <div class="project__thumb">
          <img src="images/Hydroponics.jpg" alt="Hydroponics project" />
        </div>
        <div class="project__body">
          <p class="project__tag">Project</p>
          <h3 class="project__title">Upcycled Hydroponics</h3>
          <p class="project__desc">This unit focused on using microbits/arduino to power a self sustaining hydroponics system using upcycled materials.</p>
          <div class="project__links">
            <a class="project__link" href="#">Write-up (PDF)</a>
            <a class="project__link" href="#">Photos</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="project reveal">
        <div class="project__thumb">
          <img src="images/Chess.jpg" alt="Chess project" />
        </div>
        <div class="project__body">
          <p class="project__tag">Project</p>
          <h3 class="project__title">3D modeling</h3>
          <p class="project__desc">Introducing 3D modeling to students as early as 5th grade. My pedagogy is that 3D modeling should be as important as other arts.</p>
          <div class="project__links">
            <a class="project__link" href="#">Write-up (PDF)</a>
            <a class="project__link" href="#">Photos</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

